README
-----------------------------------------
PHP Call Center
-----------------------------------------

INSTALLATION
1. Make sure you have PHP and MySQL set up correctly on your system.
2. Extract the contents of the tar file to a web published directory (particularly into a folder called phpcc).
3. Create a MySql database to be used by the application (ie. phpcc).
4. Edit connect.php with the correct MySql user, password, host, and database name.
5. From your browser, enter the URL to the install.php script.
6. If it installs successfully, enter the URL to the index.php file and log in with "1111111111".
7. Enjoy.



KNOWN ISSUES - 2022-12-20
	- Call Search currently is not functioning
	- Administrative Reports are not finished
	- Administrative DB Management not finished
	- Partial problems with other Administrative functions as well
